Package fr.cnrs.iees.twmodels

Enum LibraryTable

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<LibraryTable>
fr.cnrs.iees.twmodels.LibraryTable
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<LibraryTable>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum LibraryTable extends Enum<LibraryTable>
A lookup table for entries in ModelMaker "New" menu.

The menu display order is the declaration order in this enum. Entries are grouped as either a Template, Tutorial, Model or Test with utg and other dependencies in the form of a single zip file placed in the appropriate package.

Author:
Ian Davies - 11 Nov. 2020
